data.description: Charming 5 BR, 3 Full Bath Home Right in the heart of Midtown! Beautiful Porch, Covered Back Patio, and Huge Kitchen with appliances that all stay. Garage with an Attached Guest House/ Office that has the potential to be an excellent AirBnB opportunity with some renovation. This home is even equipped with a fully functioning Electric Vehicle Charging Station in the carport. Walking distance to Overton Square! This Midtown Home should be yours!
